Game.....: Silent Scope
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: October 25th, 2000
Ripped.......: Nothing

Release Notes
Silent Scope comes to home console systems. Get ready to experience the arcade hit on Sega Dreamcast. The President and his family have been kidnapped by lethal terrorists, and the government turns to an elite counter-terrorist sniper to neutralize the hostile threats. Your mission is to infiltrate the terrorist's headquarters, clear all areas of danger and return the President's family safely to the White House.